      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101250_Patricia_Jones/basic_info.txt:\\nstudent_id,name,address,phone,email,toefl,chinese,math,english,father_name,father_profession,mother_name,mother_profession\\n20101250,Patricia Jones,Jiang'an District, Nanjing, Oak Avenue 23,15484392773,patricia.jones92@hotmail.com,60,78.2,93.1,56.5,Christopher Jones,Engineer,Jessica Williams,Sales Representative\\n\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101250_Patricia_Jones/recommendation_letter.txt:\\nTo the Selection Committee,\\n\\nI am writing to enthusiastically recommend Patricia Jones (Student ID: 20101250) for your consideration. As Patricia Jones's academic advisor and professor for the past year, I have had the privilege of observing their growth and development as a student and individual.\\n\\nPatricia Jones has consistently demonstrated exceptional academic performance, maintaining high grades while taking challenging coursework. Their analytical abilities and attention to detail are particularly impressive. They have shown a remarkable ability to grasp complex concepts quickly and apply them effectively in practical situations.\\n\\nWhat truly distinguishes Patricia Jones is their intellectual curiosity and commitment to excellence. They are always eager to learn more and often go beyond the required coursework to explore topics in greater depth. Their research skills and ability to synthesize information from various sources are outstanding.\\n\\nIn terms of character, Patricia Jones is reliable, ethical, and demonstrates strong moral values. They are respected by their peers and have shown excellent teamwork and communication skills.\\n\\nBased on my comprehensive evaluation, I would rate Patricia Jones's overall performance as A grade level. I am confident that Patricia Jones will continue to excel in their future academic and professional endeavors.\\n\\nI give Patricia Jones my highest recommendation without reservation.\\n\\nSincerely,\\nDr. Brown\\nAssociate Professor\\nSchool of Information Technology\\nOctober 28, 2024\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101701_Isabella_Davis/basic_info.txt:\\nstudent_id,name,address,phone,email,toefl,chinese,math,english,father_name,father_profession,mother_name,mother_profession\\n20101701,Isabella Davis,Nanshan District, Beijing, Main Street 126,15070584990,isabella.davis89@gmail.com,110,74.9,83.0,62.0,David Davis,Designer,Sharon Brown,Consultant\\n\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101701_Isabella_Davis/recommendation_letter.txt:\\nTo the Selection Committee,\\n\\nI am writing to enthusiastically recommend Isabella Davis (Student ID: 20101701) for your consideration. As Isabella Davis's academic advisor and professor for the past year, I have had the privilege of observing their growth and development as a student and individual.\\n\\nIsabella Davis has consistently demonstrated exceptional academic performance, maintaining high grades while taking challenging coursework. Their analytical abilities and attention to detail are particularly impressive. They have shown a remarkable ability to grasp complex concepts quickly and apply them effectively in practical situations.\\n\\nWhat truly distinguishes Isabella Davis is their intellectual curiosity and commitment to excellence. They are always eager to learn more and often go beyond the required coursework to explore topics in greater depth. Their research skills and ability to synthesize information from various sources are outstanding.\\n\\nIn terms of character, Isabella Davis is reliable, ethical, and demonstrates strong moral values. They are respected by their peers and have shown excellent teamwork and communication skills.\\n\\nBased on my comprehensive evaluation, I would rate Isabella Davis's overall performance as S grade level. I am confident that Isabella Davis will continue to excel in their future academic and professional endeavors.\\n\\nI give Isabella Davis my highest recommendation without reservation.\\n\\nSincerely,\\nProf. Jones\\nAssociate Professor\\nSchool of Information Technology\\nNovember 19, 2024\\n\", \"annotations\": null, \"meta\": null}], \"structuredContent\": {\"content\": \"/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101250_Patricia_Jones/basic_info.txt:\\nstudent_id,name,address,phone,email,toefl,chinese,math,english,father_name,father_profession,mother_name,mother_profession\\n20101250,Patricia Jones,Jiang'an District, Nanjing, Oak Avenue 23,15484392773,patricia.jones92@hotmail.com,60,78.2,93.1,56.5,Christopher Jones,Engineer,Jessica Williams,Sales Representative\\n\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20101250_Patricia_Jones/recommendation_letter.txt:\\nTo the Selection Committee,\\n\\nI am writing to enthusiastically recommend Patricia Jones (Student ID: 20101250) for your consideration. As Patricia Jones's academic advisor and professor for the past year, I have had the privilege of observing their growth and development as a student and individual.\\n\\nPatricia Jones has consistently demonstrated exceptional academic performance, maintaining high grades while taking challenging coursework. Their analytical abilities and attention to detail are particularly impressive. They have shown a remarkable ability to grasp complex concepts quickly