ytical thinking and problem-solving skills are particularly noteworthy.\\n\\nIn terms of personal qualities, Emma Thomas is highly motivated, responsible, and shows great initiative in their studies. They are always well-prepared for class discussions and contribute meaningfully to group projects. Their ability to work effectively both independently and as part of a team makes them an ideal candidate for further academic pursuits.\\n\\nBased on my observations and Emma Thomas's academic record, I would rate their overall performance as S grade level. I have no hesitation in giving Emma Thomas my highest recommendation for any academic or professional opportunity they may pursue.\\n\\nIf you require any additional information about Emma Thomas, please do not hesitate to contact me.\\n\\nSincerely,\\nDr. Davis\\nDepartment of Computer Science\\nUniversity of Technology\\nJuly 26, 2025\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_student_database_english_talent_67526/20114869_Ethan_Martin/recommendation_letter.txt:\\nTo Whom It May Concern,\\n\\nI am writing this letter of recommendation for Ethan Martin (Student ID: 20114869), who has been my student for the past academic year. I have had the pleasure of teaching Ethan Martin in several advanced courses and have been consistently impressed by their academic performance and personal character.\\n\\nEthan Martin has demonstrated exceptional academic abilities throughout their time in my classes. They consistently achieved high grades and showed a deep understanding of the course material. Their analytical thinking and problem-solving skills are particularly noteworthy.\\n\\nIn terms of personal qualities, Ethan Martin is highly motivated, responsible, and shows great initiative in their studies. They are always well-prepared for class discussions and contribute meaningfully to group projects. Their ability to work effectively both independently and as par